<subSubSection id="62DD6540197E295D7486FF68FD1FFE40" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="2A7836CB197E295D7486FF68FE82FF27" blockId="46.[212,1172,169,424]" box="[212,320,169,192]" pageId="46" pageNumber="621">
<heading id="713081A7197E295D7486FF68FE82FF27" box="[212,320,169,192]" fontSize="10" level="3" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" reason="5">
<emphasis id="18B3EAD9197E295D7486FF68FE82FF27" box="[212,320,169,192]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="621">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2A7836CB197E295D7486FF11FD1FFE40" blockId="46.[212,1172,169,424]" pageId="46" pageNumber="621">
The male differs from 
<taxonomicName id="EDC74D48197E295D75BAFF10FDA9FF0F" authority="Santos &amp; Melo, 2014" authorityName="Santos &amp; Melo" authorityYear="2014" box="[488,619,209,232]" class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" genus="Megalopta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guarani" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis id="18B3EAD9197E295D75BAFF10FDA9FF0F" box="[488,619,209,232]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="621">M. guarani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="038057A2197E295D762AFF10FD78FF0F" box="[632,698,209,232]" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName id="EDC74D48197E295D76ADFF10FC50FF0F" authority="Santos &amp; Melo, 2014" authorityName="Santos &amp; Melo" authorityYear="2014" box="[767,914,208,232]" class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" genus="Megalopta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="karitiana" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis id="18B3EAD9197E295D76ADFF10FC50FF0F" box="[767,914,208,232]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="621">M. karitiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="038057A2197E295D77CDFF10FC20FF0F" box="[927,994,209,232]" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
by the medial protruding process of S4 digitiform in lateral view and by rugulosities present in central portion of basal area of metapostnotum; from 
<taxonomicName id="EDC74D48197E295D771CFED0FC35FECF" authority="Santos &amp; Melo, 2014" authorityName="Santos &amp; Melo" authorityYear="2014" box="[846,1015,273,296]" class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" genus="Megalopta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mapinguari" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis id="18B3EAD9197E295D771CFED0FC35FECF" box="[846,1015,273,296]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="621">M. mapinguari</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="038057A2197E295D7053FED0FB82FECF" box="[1025,1088,273,296]" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
by the mesosoma homogeneously black to brown and by medial protruding process of S4 lacking setae in the apex; from 
<taxonomicName id="EDC74D48197E295D7615FE90FD08FE8F" authority="Santos &amp; Melo, 2014" authorityName="Santos &amp; Melo" authorityYear="2014" box="[583,714,337,360]" class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" genus="Megalopta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="xavante" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis id="18B3EAD9197E295D7615FE90FD08FE8F" box="[583,714,337,360]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="621">M. xavante</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="038057A2197E295D7686FE91FCD6FE80" box="[724,788,336,359]" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
by the integument black and by presence of rugulosities in the basal area of metapostnotum. This latter character also distinguishes 
<taxonomicName id="EDC74D48197E295D7539FE51FE34FE4F" authorityName="Santos and Silveira" authorityYear="2009" box="[363,502,400,424]" class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" genus="Megalopta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="atlantica">
<emphasis id="18B3EAD9197E295D7539FE51FE34FE4F" box="[363,502,400,424]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="621">M. atlantica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<emphasis id="18B3EAD9197E295D766DFE51FD1FFE40" box="[575,733,400,423]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="621">
<taxonomicName id="EDC74D48197E295D766DFE51FD1BFE40" authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1879" box="[575,729,400,423]" class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" genus="Megalopta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="purpurata">M. purpurata</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="62DD6540197E295D7486FE25FE6FFB5E" pageId="46" pageNumber="621" type="description">
<paragraph id="2A7836CB197E295D7486FE25FE91FE1C" blockId="46.[212,1172,484,994]" box="[212,339,484,507]" pageId="46" pageNumber="621">
